          </choice><unclear>s tasya puttra</unclear><lb break="no" n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">s tat-pādānudhyāto mahādevyāṁ</supplied><unclear>ca</unclear><supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->ndra</supplied><unclear>devyā</unclear><supplied reason="lost"><!-- CHECK if <unclear> applies better.-->m utpannaḥ</supplied> <!--
